  "general_information": "The Tropic Hope is a feeder container ship built by Guangzhou Wenchong Shipyard, China. It has a gross tonnage of 15,215gt and a deadweight of 13,038dwt. The vessel is designed for temperature-controlled cargo transport in the Caribbean region and has a capacity to carry 1,148 TEU containers. It is equipped with two MacGregor cranes, a MAN B&W engine, and a high-pressure SCR system to meet Tier III NOx levels.",
